\begin_layout Section
Keyboard shortcuts
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Keyboard shortcuts are one of the most powerful tools in Lyx because they
 are fully customizable.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
Keyboard shortcuts that are often used
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate

\emph on
Note
\emph default
 with Alt+i n n
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate

\emph on
Comment
\emph default
 with Alt+i n c 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
A multi-line numbered equation with Ctrl+Alt+n (a new line is created with
 ctrl+return).
 An unnumbered environment is created with Ctrl+m return.
\end_layout

