\end_inset

Preferences
\begin_inset Formula $\rightarrow$
\end_inset

Editing
\begin_inset Formula $\rightarrow$
\end_inset

Shortcuts.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Examples: 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

math-delim | rangle
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 inserts 
\begin_inset Formula $\left|\right\rangle $
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsubsection
Command sequences
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Command sequences are explained in 
\begin_inset CommandInset href
LatexCommand href
name "command sequences"
target "http://wiki.lyx.org/Tips/CommandSequences"

\end_inset

.
 The idea is to create a useful command-shortcut than assign a keyboard
 shortcut to it.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

command-sequence cell-backward;cell-backward;cell-forward;line-end-select;line-e
nd-select;copy;newline-insert; cell-forward;cell-forward;paste;
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 copies a the recent line in a multi-line equation, example
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{eqnarray*}
\xi & = & a+\left({a\atop a}\right)+blah\\
\end{eqnarray*}

\end_inset

if the cursor is inside the second or third cell becomes
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{eqnarray*}
\xi & = & a+\left({a\atop a}\right)+blah\\
 & = & a+\left({a\atop a}\right)+blah\\
\end{eqnarray*}

\end_inset

It works in because 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

cell-backward;cell-backward;cell-forward;
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 brings the cursor to the beginning of the second cell.
 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

line-end-select;line-end-select;
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 selects the first two cells.
 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

Copy
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 is self-explanatory.
 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

newline-insert;
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 inserts a new line in the multi-line equation.
 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

cell-forward;cell-forward;
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 moves the cursor to the beginning of the second cell in the new line.
 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

Paste
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 is self-explanatory.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

command-sequence float-insert figure; char-left;up;ert-insert; self-insert
 
\backslash
centering; inset-toggle; char-right;dialog-show-new-inset graphics
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 inserts a centered figure.
\end_layout

